---
title: Panko-Crumbed Pork Katsu with Sweet Chilli Noodles & Green Beans
description: This crumbed pork katsu is absolutely delicious, and it’s also one of those dishes you can plate up to look as good as it tastes. Get ready to go pro tonight!
